<!-- ##### SECTION Title ##### -->
GwyColorButton

<!-- ##### SECTION Short_Description ##### -->
A color displaying button

<!-- ##### SECTION Long_Description ##### -->
<para>
This is GtkColorButton widget backported from Gtk+-2.4.  Or originally
was, it does not have its own colors selection dialog any more, it's just an
ordinary button displaying a color. You have to connect some callback to
its "clicked" signal. And it uses <link linkend="GwyRGBA">GwyRGBA</link>
instead of Gdk colors.
</para>

